te\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"the ongoing 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enoh also asked four questions that must be answered on why Offili's name was dropped from participating in the Women's 100m race.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Enoh\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"four questions\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"Offili's name\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"the Women's 100m race\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ofili had earlier this week disclosed she will not take part in the 100m race at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ofili\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m race\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old explained that the reason was because of administrative failures by the Athletics Federation of Nigeria, AFN, and the Nigerian Olympic Committee, NOC.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.6816777824596285, \"rank\": 0.4669676739846743, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"s